                        Research Program Plan
                        -----------------------------------------------------------------------
                    section#ResearchProgramPlan
                        .row
                            .col-xs-12
                                h2#ResearchProgramPlan Research Program Plan

                        .row
                            .col-xs-12
                                h4#ResearchPlan Research Program: Plan
                                p.text-justify
                                    | In development... Coming soon.

                                //p 詳細な研究企画 (英語):
                                    a(href='')  www.shecodez.com/research_plan.pdf
